## Backup Strategy

### Git (Primary)
```bash
# Recommended .gitignore
.obsidian/workspace.json
.obsidian/workspace-mobile.json
.obsidian/cache
.trash/
```

### Cloud Sync (Secondary)
Options:
- Obsidian Sync (official, E2E encrypted)
- iCloud/Dropbox/OneDrive (with caution)
- Syncthing (self-hosted)

**Warning**: Avoid syncing `.obsidian/` folder across multiple services simultaneously.

