## Troubleshooting

### Common Issues

| Issue | Solution |
|-------|----------|
| Dataview queries not updating | Check "Automatic View Refreshing" |
| Templates not appearing | Verify Template Folder Location |
| Git conflicts | Pull before editing, commit often |
| Slow startup | Disable unused plugins |
| Search not finding notes | Rebuild search index (Ctrl+P → "Rebuild") |

### Reset Plugin

If a plugin misbehaves:
1. Disable plugin
2. Delete plugin folder from `.obsidian/plugins/`
3. Reinstall from Community Plugins

